            sage: ((x+y)/(x-y))^2
            (x^2 + 2*x*y + y^2)/(x^2 - 2*x*y + y^2)
            sage: ((x+y)/(x-y))^-2
            (x^2 - 2*x*y + y^2)/(x^2 + 2*x*y + y^2)
            sage: ((x+y)/(x-y))^0
